		[/unit]
		[unit]
			description=_"Slim of Stature, dexterous Hands
Гўв‚¬вЂќ Seven Stones and Eleven
Left his Foes so slim a Chance
Гўв‚¬вЂќ Seven Stones and Eleven
Marksman known as Dragonbane
Гўв‚¬в„ўmongst the Statues here was slain
Гўв‚¬вЂќ Seven Stones Гўв‚¬вЂќ and the Elven
(inscribed by Gauteamus)"
