		[unit]
			description=_"A brave hero of WesnothГўв‚¬в„ўs Golden Age, this great rider and commander of men came to this evil place while on a raid against the orcs. Caught unaware by the foul creatures, many of his fellows were killed, but he fought valiantly, slaying many a foe. But alas! The foul Basilisk turned him to stone even as he slew the last orc. Now all that is left is a stark reminder of his once great bearing and strength.
(inscribed by Fynmiir)"
			facing="sw"
			name=""
