		[unit]
			description=_"The last words spoken by Grand Marshal Aethec Corryn: Гўв‚¬Е“Talael Ryndoc! I am through searching for you! I shall make my way back to HaldricГўв‚¬в„ўs Hall, and inform the court that you were too much of a coward to attend our duel! Your disgrace shall be more agonizing than the death IГўв‚¬в„ўd have given you!Гўв‚¬пїЅ

Perhaps he should not have shouted quite so loudly..."
